  "description": [
    "BISBEE ARIZONA THURSDAY MARCH 21 1957 NOW we will pay 3 on Time CertWcafes of Deposit motoring 6 months or longer Minimum Deposit 50000 Bankofugtas MEMBEK FED DEPOSIT INSURANCE CORP berries he had squeezed on feath ers and then made them into writ ing pens Togie wanted my tin whistle so bad I believe he would have given me one of his fathers horses to boot Togie told us many wild stories guess they were true He told us one Gypsy boys and girls when twelve years old get married and other Gypsys from other parts come to celebrate and they cook a steer and much wine is drunk by old and young Then the boy and girl live apart until they are 21 years old thats what the boy said I liked my Gypsy friend very much All these years later I like to lay and think of Togie in the quiet of the night which is very seldom noise on the increase Join the swing to SweptWind Get greatest advances of 1957 1 The low low 4 2foot low look of luxury that will still be fresh and new years from now when other cars start imitating it"
  ],
